title: Taxis and Public Transportation
description: The city's public transportation is provided by Dallas Area Rapid Transit (DART). Dallas Area Rapid Transit (DART) is the public transit authority for Addison, Carrollton, Cockrell Hill, Dallas, Farmers Branch, Garland, Glenn Heights, Highland Park, Irving, Richardson, Rowlett, Plano & University Park.
